## Documentation

-   <https://hepi.readthedocs.io/en/stable/>
-   <https://apn-pucky.github.io/HEPi/index.html>

## Versions

### Stable

```sh
pip install hepi [--user] [--upgrade]
```

### Dev

```sh
pip install --index-url https://test.pypi.org/simple/ hepi
```

